source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000010_OSCHON<tab>The will of the star has entrusted the future to you and yours.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000010_OSCHON<tab>Der Wille des Planeten legte die Zukunft in eure Hände ...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000020_OSCHON<tab>As entities charged with ensuring life on Etheirys, we rejoice in this outcome with all our hearts.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000020_OSCHON<tab>Wir, die dem Erhalt des Lebens auf Ætheris verschrieben sind, freuen uns darüber aus vollstem Herzen.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000030_THETWELVE<tab>'Tis time, beloved children. Time to bid farewell to we relics of the past.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000030_THETWELVE<tab>Nun nehmt Abschied, geliebte Kinder ... von uns Relikten der Ver<var 16 /var>gangen<var 16 /var>heit ...
